現職玄奘大學應用外語系專任講師學歷國立新竹教育大學臺灣語言研究與教學研究所博士班A PhD student in the Institute of Taiwan Languages and Language Teaching at National Hsinchu University of Education美國波特蘭州立大學英語教學研究所碩士MA in TESOL, Portland State University授課領域英語發音與語音學、文法與寫作、商用英語、觀光英語、多益英語研究領域英語語音學與音韻學學術著作一覽表Lin, L.-C. (2014). Effects of Phonological Awareness Training on English Word Reading among Taiwan EFL Adult Learners. Journal of Applied Foreign Languages, 21, 23-41. (國立高雄第一科技大學應用外語學報第二十一期)Lin, L.-H., & Lin, L.-C. (2014). An investigation of later-life planning by different generation in Taiwan. Educational Gerontology, 40(8), 557-571.Lin, L.-C. (2012a). The effects of phonological awareness training on English reading. Proceedings of 2012 International Conference on Language Instruction and Cultural Exchange, 101-112. (Hsuan Chuang University)Lin, L.-C. (2012b). In J. Colpaert, A. Aerts, W.-C. Wu, & Y.-C. Chao (Eds.), The effects of phonological awareness training with computer-assisted instruction on English word reading in L1 Chinese university students. 2012 The 15th International CALL Research Conference: The Medium Matters (pp. 425-430). Taichung, Taiwan: Providence University.Lin, L.-C. (2012c). 發明專利第I 357587號。專利名稱：一種多音節英文字彙語音音節劃分方法Phonetic Syllabification。Lin, L.-C. (2011). Fundamental generalizations of English syllabification. Concentric: Studies in Linguistics, 37(2), 179-208.Lin, L.-C. (2010a). The effects of phonological awareness training on L1 Chinese university students’ English vocabulary retention. Hsuan Chuang Humanities Journal, 10, 117-134. Hsinchu, Taiwan: Hsuan Chuang University.Lin, L.-C. (2010b). In W.-Y. Dai, C.-S. Hsia, Y.-N. Leung, & H.-C. Lee (Eds.), The effect of phonological awareness training with computer-aided instruction on English vocabulary retention. Constructing new strategies for English instruction (pp. 187-201). Taipei, Taiwan: Crane.Lin, L.-C. (2008a). The effect of instruction in syllabication and phonics on English vocabulary learning. Proceedings of LTL 2008: The First Conference on Language Teaching and Linguistics, 49-62.Lin, L.-C. (2008b). 超級英文拼音法Phonics & phonetics (2nd ed.). Taipei, Taiwan: Tunghua.Lin, L.-C. & Wu, J.-C. (2006a). In Y.-N. Leung, M. Jenks, & C.-S. Hsia (Eds.), The effect of syllabication on English vocabulary teaching to Chinese students. New aspects of English language teaching and learning (pp. 190-200). Taipei, Taiwan: Crane.Lin, L.-C. (2006b). 超級英文拼音法Phonics & phonetics. Taipei, Taiwan: Tunghua.Lin, L.-C. (2003). Teaching English grapheme-phoneme correspondence. Hsuan Chuang Humanities Journal, 1, 243-253. Hsinchu, Taiwan: Hsuan Chuang University.








